<XDL>

<Blueprint id="Formation_of_phenylboronic_acid_pinacol_ester_by_Amination">

  <Parameters>
      <Parameter id='reaction_time' type='time' value='5 h'/>
      <Parameter id='reaction_temp' type='temp' value='90 Â°C'/>
      <Parameter id="amine_equiv" type="equiv" value="1.0 eq" />
      <Parameter id="boronic_acid_equiv" type="equiv" value="1.3 eq" />
      <Parameter id="catalyst_equiv" type="equiv" value="0.05 eq"/> 
      <Parameter id="ligand_equiv" type="equiv" value="0.05 eq"/>
      <Parameter id="workup_volume_1" type="volume" value="15 mL" />
      <Parameter id="workup_volume_2" type="volume" value="20 mL" />
  </Parameters>

  <Hardware>
   <Component id="reactor" type="reactor" />
   <Component id="rotavap" type="rotavap" />
   <Component id="separator" type="flask" />
   <Component id="Cartridge_Celite" type="cartridge" chemical="Celite" />
   <Component id="Cartridge_MgSO4" type="cartridge" chemical="MgSO4" />
   <Component id="flask_Nitrogen_1" type="flask" />
   <Component id="flask_Nitrogen_2" type="flask" />
   <Component id="flask_Block" type="flask" />


  </Hardware>
  
  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="boronic_acid"
      inchi="1S/C12H16BBrO2/c1-11(2)12(3,4)16-13(15-11)9-5-7-10(14)8-6-9/h5-8H,1-4H3"
      molecular_formula="C12H16BBrO2"
      molecular_weight="282.97 g/mol"
      role="substrate"
      solid="True" /> 
    <Reagent
      id="amine"
      solid="True"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      id="catalyst"
      solid="True"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      id="ligand"
      solid="True"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      id="base"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      id="quenching_solvent"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      id="reaction_solvent"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      id="general_solvent"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      id="washing_solvent_1"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      id="washing_solvent_2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      id="extraction_solvent"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure base_scale="2.5 mmol / eq">
    
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="extraction_solvent" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="reaction_solvent" />
    
    <Purge
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="amine"
      amount="amine_equiv" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="catalyst"
      amount="catalyst_equiv" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ligand"
      amount="ligand_equiv" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="boronic_acid"
      amount="boronic_acid_equiv"/> 
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="reaction_solvent"
      aspiration_speed="20"
      amount="10.0 mL / eq" />
    <!-- purge the solution with inert gas -->
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="30 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="base"
      aspiration_speed="20"
      amount="3.5 mL / eq" 
      time="3 min"
      flush_solvent="reaction_solvent"
      flush_solvent_volume="3 mL"
      stir="True" /> 
     <!-- mix the reagent before heating-->
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="10 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="reaction_temp"
      time="reaction_time"
      stir= "true" />
    <HeatChillReturnToRT
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="extraction_solvent"
      volume="workup_volume_2"
      stir="True" />    
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="quenching_solvent"
      volume="workup_volume_1"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="0.5 h" />
    <Transfer
      stir_to_vessel="True"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      through="Cartridge_Celite" 
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="extraction_solvent"
      rinsing_volume="workup_volume_2"
      rinsing_repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="washing_solvent_1"
      solvent_volume="workup_volume_1"
      repeats="1" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="washing_solvent_2"
      solvent_volume="workup_volume_1"
      repeats="1" />  
    <Transfer
      from_vessel='separator'
      to_vessel='rotavap'
      through="Cartridge_MgSO4" 
      volume='all'
      rinsing_solvent='extraction_solvent'
      rinsing_volume='workup_volume_2'
      rinsing_repeats='1'/>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 Â°C"
      pressure="350 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 Â°C"
      pressure="100 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="extraction_solvent"/>
  </Procedure>
</Blueprint>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor_1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id='flask_Nitrogen_1'
      type='flask' />
    <Component
      id='flask_Nitrogen_2'
      type='flask' />
    <Component
      id='flask_Block'
      type='flask' />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="Cartridge_Celite"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="Celite" />
      <Component
      id="Cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="Substituted amine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-Bromophenylboronic acid pinacol ester"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Pd(OAc)2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Tri-tert-butyl-phosphonium tetrafluoroborate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="LiHMDS in Toluene(1M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Toluene"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="EtOAc"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="NH4Cl solution"
      role="solvent" />
      <Reagent
      name="NaCl solution"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
  <!-- Step 1 -->
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="EtOAc" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="Toluene" />
    <CConnect
      from_vessel="flask_Nitrogen_2"
      to_vessel="reactor_1" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor_1"
      time="10 min"/>
    <CConnect
      from_vessel="flask_Block"
      to_vessel="reactor_1" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="Substituted amine"
      mass="0.49 g" 
      confirm_solid="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="4-Bromophenylboronic acid pinacol ester"
      mass="0.85 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="Pd(OAc)2"
      mass="28 mg" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="Tri-tert-butyl-phosphonium tetrafluoroborate"
      mass="36 mg"
      confirm_solid="True" /> 
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="Toluene"
      volume="10.0 mL" 
      time="1 min"
      priming_volume="3 mL"/>
    <CConnect
      from_vessel="flask_Nitrogen_2"
      to_vessel="reactor_1" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor_1"
      time="30 min"
      continue_stirring="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="LiHMDS in Toluene(1M)"
      volume="3.5 mL" 
      time="3 min"
      priming_volume="3 mL"/> 
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="Toluene"
      volume="3.0 mL" 
      time="1 min"
      priming_volume="3 mL"/>
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="90 Â°C"
      time="2 h" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="25 Â°C"
      time="0.5 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="EtOAc"
      volume="30 mL"
      time="2 min"
      stir="True" /> 
    <!-- Quench the LiHMDS/>-->   
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="Water"
      volume="15 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor_1"
